# perf_bench_capped.shot — M6 P03 perf bench, "internal_h 1080" path.
#
# Same scene as perf_bench.shot but with the internal cap on (1080
# lines). World + post-process rasterise into a 2580×1080 RT; the
# upscale to the 3440×1440 window is a cheap bilinear blit. The
# expectation is FPS is materially higher than the no-cap baseline.

window 3440 1440
seed   2 7
out    build/shots/perf_bench_capped

internal_h 1080
perf_overlay on

extra_chassis Heavy   1200 920
extra_chassis Scout   1300 920
extra_chassis Sniper  1400 920
extra_chassis Engineer 1500 920

aim 700 920

at  30 press jet
at 120 release jet
at 150 press jet
at 240 release jet
at 270 press jet
at 360 release jet
at 390 press jet
at 480 release jet

at  60 shot t060
at 180 shot t180
at 300 shot t300
at 420 shot t420
at 540 shot t540
at 600 end
